org.apache.lucene.spatial.spatial4j

Class Geo3dShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.spatial.spatial4j.Geo3dShape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.spatial4j.core.shape.Shape

    public class Geo3dShape
extends Object
implements com.spatial4j.core.shape.Shape
    A Spatial4j Shape wrapping a GeoShape ("Geo3D") -- a 3D planar geometry based Spatial4j Shape implementation. Geo3D implements shapes on the surface of a sphere or ellipsoid.
    WARNING: This API is experimental and might change in incompatible ways in the next release.

      • ROUNDOFF_ADJUSTMENT

        protected static final double ROUNDOFF_ADJUSTMENT
